```gitignore
# Terraform
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json
!example.tfvars

# Terragrunt
.terragrunt-cache/
terragrunt-debug.tfvars.json

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes

# IDE
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/

# Secrets
*.pem
*.key
secrets.auto.tfvars
```

This covers Terraform state and cache files, Terragrunt cache, macOS system files, common IDE artifacts, and sensitive files like keys. Save this as `.gitignore` in your project root.
